Package BIF.SWE1.plugins

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorPlugin
    The Error plugin is responsible to return a 404 page if no other plugin can handle the request.
    NaviPlugin
    Is capable of searching for city names based on an entered street name
    StaticPlugin
    "StaticPlugin" is a full-functional, low priority plugin for loading static files.
    TemperaturePlugin
    Is capable of running a simulated sensor that reads the current temperature and accessing a H2 Database that contains 10.000 temperature data sets
    TestPlugin  
    ToLowerPlugin
    Is capable of transforming a String to a lowercase String
